claim: Lil Wayne's sixth album is unnamed.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Recording sessions for the album began in late 2008 , shortly after Lil Wayne 's sixth studio album , Tha Carter III  (  2008  )  was released to strong sales and critical acclaim : however , the sessions were put on hold , as Lil Wayne claimed he did not want to follow an album he held in high regard so quickly with another , potentially inferior release .
